Career








 work with us 
  
  

We are looking for excellence We are always looking for ambitious people, be they career starters or experiences profiles, and who are passionate about Ferrari and automotive excellence. Career opportunities

   




 Ferrari values 

Important values We are a unique team, connected by the same values. We work for the same goals: to win challenges on markets and circuits around the world. to learn more





Individual & Team
Our individual people are our strongest asset.

to learn more
                          




Emotion & Integrity
We live our company with enthusiasm, with a strong sense of pride and with emotion.

to learn more
                          




Tradition &  Innovation
Representing a reality where tradition and innovation are constant drivers for renewal of the Ferrari legend

to learn more
                          




Passion & Exellence
For us passion means working “with your heart” as well as with your head. 

to learn more
                          



   




 formula uomo 
 

 
  
  

Best place  to work Ferrari knows that the best individual and team performance is only achieved if employees feel they are in the right place, the right environment. to learn more

   




 Ferrari selection process 
 

 
  
  

Hiring talented individuals for long term  development and performance We have high expectations, for individuals with confirmed skills as well as the ability and ambition to develop in the future. to learn more

   













